Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自遥远太空的未知生物 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拥有人类所无法理解的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现在这个星球上已有40年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大半个世界都沦为了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已进入战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60秒后降落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循作战计划 迅速投身前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认射出板已固定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收到导航信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出轨道 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aloha, Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(557,655)}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮丝搞不好会去跟敌人求爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真想被金色的宇宙人求爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是经过严格训练筛选出的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到十分骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二号机 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比报告上写的还糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Second machine Olympia-Angels, landing check
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(640,655)}二号机 Olympia-Angels着陆确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要像哥哥这样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(685,655)\fs30}Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四号机 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对Festum专用思维控制体感操纵式载人兵器法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1037,655)\fs30}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被选中的人才能操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Type1 Type2 Type3 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意Type4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内置敌人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其力量为人类所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们早就灭亡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便还远远无法取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也用它争取到了萌生希望的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用的！
Comment: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【XXXX sword, launch】【4：20
