Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根机呼叫高德小队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(698,655)}Gold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(496,655)}Morgan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在开始投身前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 别通信！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗语的变动全都被敌人知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高层太小看敌人的读心能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里想什么全都瞒不过敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒纳凯阿巡逻基地崩塌
