Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：夏威夷岛上的五座火山之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部机能…都被敌人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧引导平民疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有部队集结到北部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一防卫队被歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距本岛最终防卫线还有两公里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(455,655)}Big Island
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧 那雷恩将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(643,655)}Narain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是太平洋圈最大的运输基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦这里被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百万人都会饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么都要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们学习了之前不屑一顾的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习了人类是如何自保的吗 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能登机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们可都逼到眼前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急 马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒纳凯阿不会有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十号机严重损毁 乔治被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停下 照作战计划进行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现高德小队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Left wing detached, recalculating balance control
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(640,655)}左翼分离 重新计算平衡控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是敌人！他们被敌人同化了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克 切断罗伯的右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 在 那 里 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯 快脱离 罗伯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然钻进我的心里来了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯居然…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Navigation system, failure
