Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘 光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部发布交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布对象为本岛全域！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…！
