Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剥夺沃尔特少校的职权 即刻逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,655)\fs30}Walter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雷恩将军命令中止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入坐标 进入攻击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我的战友…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都去搜寻生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质问者型…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(596,655)}Sphinx
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我攻击了友军…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了…有人活着吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我们赢不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 究竟是为了什么 为了什么而战的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旷日持久的战争让世界凋敝不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够理解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争是否也就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的角落中等待破土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是日本在战乱中毁灭之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为传承和平这一文化而建造的人工岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾经的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地区大赛就快到了 鼓起干劲来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香明白 要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香美香 你可别出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续继续…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她就想起过去的一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 回去的时候上一骑那儿吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你讨厌我做的饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}堂马广登特别节目 追踪神秘巨型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢广登是做了多少节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹也是太有奉陪精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 无聊透顶 天气还热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我想去Alvis上班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别光学打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得继承岛上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那起码装个空调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好 里奈前辈…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事 镝木？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你不是昨天就买过这本了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那个…这本是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说镝木 你是学生会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道买漫画 七夕祭典的准备都做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个…里奈前辈不在讨论就没法进行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够不争气的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然下次到一骑前辈那里一起讨论？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 里奈前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我在上班啊 怎么可能会有空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是机体的设计 更要学习实际组装时的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ改 上臂引擎安装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进行FTP试验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接确认完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越熟练了呢 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(788,655)\fs30}Kanon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了妈妈的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里可是职员兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出去吃个饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天待在这儿要闷出病来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想去一骑那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒无所谓…去哪里都成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不希望再有人驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又要把它组装起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到卡农会去学工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年纪技术却很了得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是想做你徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干脆退休算了 毕竟还得画这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是驾驶员培养教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊 西尾老师开口的事没法推托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老规矩 去吃咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 会赶不上午市的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有问题的 让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御门的 东西我搬到里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老爸教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个 一骑哥 有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 你来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午的研究收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子准备还没好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过会儿再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧 吃饭是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是 不过菜名加上厨师的名字是这里的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如一骑咖喱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沟口先生擅自加的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很尊敬一骑前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见和沟口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我还以为能和远见前辈一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已捕捉到不明机体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}unknown follow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入自动瞄准程序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:22:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这招怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定目标 发射导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Fox-One
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你超前了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}run out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因为自己飞得快就把敌人给超了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又输给沟口先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要是实战 就是我被打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace 申请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK Arrows 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(748,655)}lead again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}will-call
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你别这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 坐在大飞机上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽她啊 最近总是这样净跟幻想中的朋友说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为没有同龄的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得不用太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很感性 所以我就是放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐在飞机上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了呢 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,655)\fs30}Emery
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.84,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极其一般
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.23,0:24:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来教你什么是料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比预定温度还高了两度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.46,0:24:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要修正才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人啊 真是笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:24:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐套餐两份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.46,0:25:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是皆城炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我们没点这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 卖相还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.81,0:25:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一堆男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连总士都上阵了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.10,0:25:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农是蜜瓜雪顶和…请用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.44,0:25:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么啊 我可没点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.07,0:25:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费赠送
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你常常来光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.89,0:25:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是不…讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有30次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.09,0:25:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复诊是在下星期 别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.26,0:25:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的成人礼也是那时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可得来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 总是承蒙你关照了 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:25:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下次见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.97,0:26:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心完我的身体就开始担心一骑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.96,0:26:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 总是操心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.79,0:26:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹也做做自己想做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.57,0:26:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.89,0:26:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如跟你一起吃吃饭什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.90,0:26:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.78,0:26:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见学航空 卡农学工科 剑司学医疗 要投身教育
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都决定了各自的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.46,0:26:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士你搞研究吗 感觉挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.68,0:26:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？在咖啡馆当厨师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 还挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.58,0:26:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想让当年的王牌驾驶员的宝贵经验发挥余热
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.28,0:26:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当教官也是个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些痕迹 不开法芙娜了也还是留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是尼伯龙根连接导致的小规模同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(433,655)\fs30}Nibelungen
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.68,0:26:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会找到治疗方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始学些什么 做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.71,0:27:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后这些事却以未完成收场 我不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.49,0:27:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这样的吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.44,0:27:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有希望恢复的 别太悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.85,0:27:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.20,0:27:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.24,0:27:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么长的时间 足够我做心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.19,0:27:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何况现在眼睛也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是和平安稳的 重要的伙伴生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.14,0:27:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我会一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.62,0:27:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.04,0:27:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去下层区域吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在去生物圈的实验室之前看看乙姬的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(457,655)}biosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.13,0:27:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上你读的是博士课程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改成特种医疗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.85,0:28:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生对我说 这两方面都是照顾乙姬所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.48,0:28:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.73,0:28:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.53,0:28:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和乙姬为我们所做的事相比
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.62,0:28:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界还在继续战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.64,0:28:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据所罗门的应答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战火反倒是扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.66,0:28:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬明明那么渴望和平
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.17,0:28:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太令人悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.06,0:29:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.49,0:29:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你一直保护着这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.67,0:29:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.22,0:29:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对什么东西起反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.85,0:29:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 不明机体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.85,0:29:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：CDC=作战指挥中心(Combat Direction Center)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.53,0:29:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,90秒后将到达防护罩外沿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.53,0:29:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,655)\fs30}Shield Line
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.31,0:29:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标已进入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.31,0:29:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标情报入库 比对结果
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,655)\fs30}Target Merge
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.88,0:29:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-300 Super Galaxy 目标为人类军大型运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.71,0:29:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军…？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感应到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.95,0:30:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个十分美丽的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.71,0:30:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.28,0:30:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.86,0:30:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾梅莉好像也感应到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.68,0:30:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让我们见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.46,0:30:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫CDC 紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 维持距离跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,655)\fs30}Follow Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.55,0:31:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到训练中的红隼战斗机报告
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,655)\fs30}Kestrel
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.80,0:31:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军运输机正在靠近 紧急事态发生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于防护罩外确认到质量不明的回转体
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(901,655)}worm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门系统没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,655)\fs30}Shlomo
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有机库启动迎击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,655)\fs30}burg
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1 第2重力波防护罩已展开
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,655)\fs30}Welle Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.92,0:31:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航路不变 法芙娜准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.45,0:31:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动手 敌人还没有发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.18,0:31:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军只是在一味地逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放他们离开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住区传来通信请求 是日野家发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.44,0:31:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.40,0:31:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.24,0:31:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.84,0:31:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她说请救助那架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}拜托了 妈妈 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}别担心 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.89,0:31:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要激动 正在帮你问了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.36,0:31:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}今天有工作的人员请立即进入应急态势
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.80,0:31:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}各位岛民请勿外出 等待最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.85,0:31:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}随着应急体制的启动 第一……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.91,0:31:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}防御幕墙已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.91,0:31:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\pos(575,60)\fs30}waffeladen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.42,0:32:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}向岛防卫线 刚瑠岛控制区……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,200)\frz22\frx12\fry-12}出击要求播报
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕果然棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.19,0:31:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说彗 同样的杂志你昨天就买过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.32,0:31:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.56,0:31:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改成出击要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段视频的灯光打得一般般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.59,0:32:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别录太多版啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.43,0:32:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说要实战 我们是不是也能驾驶法芙娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.09,0:32:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接测试都没做过就上？应该只是观战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.99,0:32:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 我都还没像广登前辈那样做好头盔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西根本不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.17,0:32:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.01,0:32:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.25,0:32:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的前辈留给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.54,0:32:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广登前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.13,0:32:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.74,0:32:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.65,0:32:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.30,0:32:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把护身头盔给她没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.26,0:32:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们能开法芙娜的时间也没剩几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.07,0:32:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁现在让她继承了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.07,0:33:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.41,0:33:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能主动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.28,0:33:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.95,0:33:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门系统发出应答 敌人很可能在200秒内实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.25,0:33:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向50° 减速航行 防护罩部分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.19,0:33:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红隼战斗机引导运输机降落到海面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.43,0:33:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC呼叫Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.07,0:33:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请按流程开始引导运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.07,0:33:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(802,655)}track
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.04,0:33:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.10,0:33:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.19,0:33:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入代码 伪装镜面解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.73,0:33:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是岛 真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.67,0:33:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.52,0:34:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始毕业考试
